      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pump Pressure Rise Validation — Operating Curve Agreement",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pump pressure rise was compared against manufacturer-supplied hydraulic performance data across the five CPB operating points. Predicted values agreed within 5% of measured values at all points.",
