      "description": "CFD-predicted wall shear stress distributions in the volute region were compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements from a scaled water-glycerol analog model. Spatial agreement was assessed using a validation metric based on area-weighted RMS deviation, yielding a normalized error of 6.8%, within the 10% acceptance threshold.",
